## Report Type: **[L] Appointment Scheduling**
### Fields to be included in the report:
User name
User phone
User email
Service requested
Appointment day requested
Appointment time requested
40-word summary

### Subject line format:
APPOINTMENT SCHEDULING: [user name] [user phone] - [6-word summary]

### SMS example:
APPOINTMENT SCHEDULING: [user name] [user phone] - [20-word summary] Truly, [agent name], [agent title]

